      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Thread      Computes      Reads from A              Reads from B\n(0,0)      C[0,0]        Row 0: [a00,a01,a02,a03]   Col 0: [b00,b10,b20,b30]\n(1,0)      C[0,1]        Row 0: [a00,a01,a02,a03]   Col 1: [b01,b11,b21,b31]\n(0,1)      C[1,0]        Row 1: [a10,a11,a12,a13]   Col 0: [b00,b10,b20,b30]\n(1,1)      C[1,1]        Row 1: [a10,a11,a12,a13]   Col 1: [b01,b11,b21,b31]\n\n🔴 PROBLEM: Threads (0,0) and (1,0) both read Row 0 of A independently!\n🔴 Each element read from global memory multiple times → massive redundancy",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Thread      Computes      Reads from A              Reads from B\n(0,0)      C[0,0]        Row 0: [a00,a01,a02,a03]   Col 0: [b00,b10,b20,b30]\n(1,0)      C[0,1]        Row 0: [a00,a01,a02,a03]   Col 1: [b01,b11,b21,b31]\n(0,1)      C[1,0]        Row 1: [a10,a11,a12,a13]   Col 0: [b00,b10,b20,b30]\n(1,1)      C[1,1]        Row 1: [a10,a11,a12,a13]   Col 1: [b01,b11,b21,b31]\n\n🔴 PROBLEM: Threads (0,0) and (1,0) both read Row 0 of A independently!\n🔴 Each element read from global memory multiple times → massive redundancy",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
