      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "✓ CORRECT: Each thread independently computes its output element\n✓ CORRECT: Bounds check prevents out-of-bounds access\n✓ CORRECT: Dot product is computed accurately\n\n✗ SLOW: No data reuse — same elements read many times\n✗ SLOW: Uncoalesced memory access — inefficient patterns\n✗ SLOW: Memory-bound — 95% time waiting for data, 5% computing\n\nSOLUTION: Tiled version loads blocks into shared memory ONCE and reuses them across 16 threads",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "✓ CORRECT: Each thread independently computes its output element\n✓ CORRECT: Bounds check prevents out-of-bounds access\n✓ CORRECT: Dot product is computed accurately\n\n✗ SLOW: No data reuse — same elements read many times\n✗ SLOW: Uncoalesced memory access — inefficient patterns\n✗ SLOW: Memory-bound — 95% time waiting for data, 5% computing\n\nSOLUTION: Tiled version loads blocks into shared memory ONCE and reuses across 16 threads",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
